Subject: [PATCH 17/17] KVM: arm/arm64: vgic: Allow more than 256 vcpus for
 KVM_IRQ_LINE
Date: Mon,  9 Sep 2019 14:48:07 +0100
Message-Id: <20190909134807.27978-18-maz@kernel.org>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.20.1
